OL,3,CAssisted dying in Jersey: A step
OL,4,Ccloser to being legalised
OL,6,FIn the proposals, they are known as
OL,7,Froute 1 and route 2.
OL,9,FRoute 1 would allow for assisted dying
OL,10,Fwhen the individual has been diagnosed
OL,11,Fwith a terminal physical illness,
OL,12,Fwhich is likely to cause their death
OL,13,Fwithin six months or 12 months in the
OL,14,Fcase of neurodegenerative conditions.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
