OL,3,CAssisted dying in Jersey: A step
OL,4,Ccloser to being legalised
OL,6,FThe proposition also stresses that no
OL,7,Fislander would be legally bound to
OL,8,Fparticipate in the provision of
OL,9,Fassisted dying.
OL,11,FIt also underlines the importance of a
OL,12,Fminimum timeframe between the moment
OL,13,Fan individual requests an assisted
OL,14,Fdeath, and the actual day of death.
OL,16,FAccording to the proposals, it is
OL,17,Fdifficult to accurately estimate the
OL,18,Fnumber of assisted deaths there would
OL,19,Fbe in Jersey if the plans were passed.
